data.title: Richest Tennis Players in The World (Net Worth & Prize Money)
data.meta_description: Who are the richest tennis players in the world right now? Find out who's earned the most in prize money and who's invested wisely!
data.text:
11. Victoria Azarenka â€“ Net Worth: $28.2 Million

Victoria Azarenka is currently the world number 7 female tennis player. She had to retire from the last tournament, Roland Garros, as she was suffering from injury. Little did she know, she was already pregnant! In July 2016, she announced this wonderful news.

Victoria Azarenka, also known as Vika, was born in July 31, 1989. She started playing tennis when she was seven years old. And she started her professional career in tennis in 2003. Throughout her thirteen years of professional tennis, she has earned a total of $28,244,443 prize money.

Like most top ten players, Vika is endorsed by international brands such as Nike, Red Bull energy drink, and Citizen watchmaker.

Vika said she will be back in playing tennis after the birth of her first child. In the meantime, she can enjoy the millions of dollars she has earned and focus on her pregnancy.
